text: "Got a Little Crazy" is a song by Kenny Chesney. ==Music video== It premiered on CMT on October 3, 2008. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of October 31, 2008. ==References== Category:2007 songs Category:Kenny Chesney songs Category:Music videos directed by Shaun Silva
title: Got a Little Crazy
